title: Dj.Nece's International DJ Mix 2
description:
Well here is my second Idj Mix I hope you enjoy this one too. This is my track listing from my mix I hope you like the tracks and the way they were assembled. The acapellas and sound effects were not included.

1.	Maine-Narcotic
2.	Angel Moraes-Tribal Function
3.	Depeche Mode-Sinner In Me
4.	Da Souza Feat. Shena-Guilty
5.	WaWa Vs Eric Smax & Thomas Gold Feat. Hilary Duff-Stranger
6.	Eric Smax & Thomas Gold-Fake This Feeling
7.	Noel Sinner-Pull Over
8.	David Guetta-Love Is Gone
9.	Ian Carey & Mochico Feat. Ms. Bunty-Say What You Want
10.	Satoshie Tomie-Scandal In New York
11.	Destiny?s Child-Loose My Breath
12.	Razor & Guido-Bohemian Rhapsody
13.	Eddie Amador-Eleanor Wigby
14.	Tiesto & BT-Break My Fall
15.	Coldplay-Trouble
16.	Quiver-Everything?s Not You
17.	Brian Cross-Sunny Rain

Thank you for your time and your patience I am hoping that you will bare with me on the mixes and see the idea of it all. I will place a new one every month now ok so see you in July 2008. For feed back on anything just get at me at the following:
